name: Unidentified_Hutt_sister
content:
A Hutt female alongside her twin brother, attempted to claim Jabba Desilijic Tiure's criminal empire after the death of Bib Fortuna.
Around 9 ABY, the female Hutt and her brother met with Boba Fett outside of the Sanctuary in an attempt to make their claim for Jabba's criminal empire. Afterwards they sent Krrsantan to kill Boba Fett, although they failed. The following day the Twins arrived in Boba Fett's Palace to apologize for the assassination attempt and they gave him a rancor. Eventually she and her brother left Tatooine after they learned Jabba's territory was promised to the Pyke Syndicate by Mayor Mok Shaiz.
According to her brother, this female Hutt was less patient and was upset by Fett's refusal to obey them.
The Hutt sister first appeared in the episode "Chapter 2: The Tribes of Tatooine" of the Disney+ series The Book of Boba Fett on January 5, 2022. According to the Simplified and Traditional Chinese subtitles of the episode on Disney+, the female Hutt is the male Hutt's younger sister . The line is spoken in Huttese, regardless of the language a viewer chooses for audio.
In an interview with TVLine, Ming-Na Wen and Temuera Morrison revealed that cardboard cutouts were used on set to represent the Hutts that would eventually be realized through computer-generated imagery. Morrison also stated that his stand-in, JJ Dashnaw or "Jimmy," provided dialogue for the Twins during filming.
